<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: 「Necro Maiden」Mei -->
  <RI_Storyteller_ZombieGirl.label>「冥娘」梅花</RI_Storyteller_ZombieGirl.label>
  <!-- EN: Mei was born into a wealthy family amid wartime. Gifted with extraordinary talent, she was nevertheless regarded as an embodiment of misfortune and calamity due to congenital illness and tragedies within her family, and she died at a young age. At the moment of her death, intense resentment and unwillingness drew the attention of a curse; she was not consumed by it, but instead became suspended between life and death.\n\nMei harbors deep hatred toward humanity. Within the highly random flow of the story, she may act like a child throwing tantrums—deliberately causing trouble and singling out your characters. -->
  <RI_Storyteller_ZombieGirl.description>梅花出生于战乱中的富裕家庭，天赋卓绝，却因先天疾病与家中事件被视为不幸与灾厄的化身，最终芳龄早逝。死亡的瞬间，强烈的怨恨与不甘，引来了诅咒，她未被其吞噬，而是停留在生死之间。\n\n梅花对人类充满恨意，在充满随机性的故事节奏下，会像小孩一般捣乱，故意针对你的角色。</RI_Storyteller_ZombieGirl.description>
  
</LanguageData>